title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell.
description: An exception is being thrown during the process of exporting data from a table that is contained within a grid cell.
OB: Upon attempting to export data from a table within a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export process for data in a table within a grid cell should proceed without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Insert a table into one grid cell.
2. Insert another table into a different grid cell.
3. Attempt to export data from one of the tables within the grid cells.
